==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Grip
<hw>Grip</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. AS. <ets>grip</ets> furrow,
hitch, D. <ets>greb</ets>.]</ety> <def>A small ditch or furrow.</def>
<rj><au>Ray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
